/// Per-user, per-table column preferences (sort / hidden / frozen / widths)
/// for QuikScale list pages. Lives inside app_quikscale (NOT auth.User) so
/// adding a new table to the app doesn't require touching the shared User
/// model. Migrates the legacy User.kpiFrozenCol / User.priorityFrozenCol /
/// User.wwwFrozenCol (and matching) columns — those stay in place for
/// rollback safety but are no longer read by the app.
